This year in Cape Town was no different and the following companies received the best stand accolade: ZEST Music, Du Plessis and Curran, Boschendal, Rickety Bridge, Sarah Isaacs Photography, Zonnevanger, Mr & Mrs M, JC Events and Infinity Dress. In addition to the look of the stand, the judges look for the impact and originality of the stand, the quality and finish of the implementation, accessibility to the stand, the presentation of their brand and the message that the visitor will receive and lastly, the neatness and appearance of both the stand and the staff on the stand.